# Full-Stack Todo App

A full-stack todo app with user authentication and real-time task management.

## Live Demo
https://fullstack-todo-frontend-iota.vercel.app

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React
- Backend: Node.js + Express
- Auth: JWT + bcrypt
- Deployed: Vercel (frontend) + Railway (backend)

## Features
- Register and login securely
- Add, complete, and delete tasks
- Tasks saved per user account
- Fully deployed and live
